longBusinessSummary: Gencan Capital Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the solar energy generation business in Ontario, Canada. The company was formerly known as Genterra Energy Inc. and changed its name to Gencan Capital Inc. in August 2015. Gencan Capital Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada. Gencan Capital Inc. is a subsidiary of Genterra Capital Inc.
